 ('116', '153', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Margo Lynch\",\"slug\":\"margo-lynch\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"mlynch@sonica-fitout.com\",\"71\":\"\",\"66\":\"A large part of my role is looking after the administrative activities of the company to ensure the smooth running of our office on a daily basis. I also look after the accounts and work closely with our Surveying Team and accountants to ensure our accounts are kept fully up to date.\",\"70\":[\"181\"],\"65\":\"Office Manager\",\"68\":\"I love being part of a team and Sonica gives me that. Working on the accounts gives me the opportunity to be involved in each project and see how it all comes together.\",\"67\":\"By choosing Sonica you know your project is in the right hands, all employees are passionate about the company and show the same drive, motivation and commitment on every project no matter how big or small it is. Sonica has a proven track record and clients come back to us because they know they can entrust their project to us.\"}}', '2018-02-15 17:57:57', '2018-02-15 17:57:57', 'a4290b3b-044b-4d3f-8f59-4921edc0b271'),
 ('117', '154', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Alin Buzgo\",\"slug\":\"alin-buzgo\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"-\",\"71\":\"\",\"66\":\"As Site Manager, my role is to maintain quality control procedures, check and verify site reports, meet and supervise subcontractor site staff and to make regular and routine safety inspections to ensure overall construction site safety. l also liaise with Clients and the Professional Team on progress reporting, producing detailed weekly reports through our customised Construction Management applications for issue at the weekly site meetings.\",\"70\":[\"161\"],\"65\":\"Site Manager\",\"68\":\"Setting high goals at the start of each project, and working hard to motivate the Team around me to achieve them.\",\"67\":\"Treating each project as unique, Sonica Fitout develops individual plans to contribute to and meet the tailored requirements of each project and Client. Our experienced Team ensures that our Clients consistently get the highest quality end product.\"}}', '2018-02-15 17:58:09', '2018-02-15 17:58:09', '20fe5efa-6780-40f9-8375-b31f935a21ec'),
 ('118', '155', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Marc McHugh\",\"slug\":\"marc-mchugh\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"mmchugh@sonica-fitout.com\",\"71\":\"\",\"66\":\"As Site Manager, my role is to oversee all aspects includes of H&S on site, carrying out risk assessments, issuing permits of work and attending all progress meetings with site team and subcontractors to ensure all the Client needs are met. My responsibility is also to take care of work implementation and quality control measures.\",\"70\":[\"179\"],\"65\":\"Site Manager\",\"68\":\"Working with subcontractors on both large and small construction sites with tight deadlines.\",\"67\":\"Sonica is one of the top companies in the Fitout game with number of awards. By choosing Sonica, you sign up for a high level of both standard and commitment from all members of the Sonica family. Sonica provide the next level in fitout and will leave you with a product that will last a life time.\"}}', '2018-02-15 17:58:18', '2018-02-15 17:58:18', 'aa72cd18-2104-402b-ac90-fe0789cfa9ec'),
 ('119', '156', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Eliska Valtrova\",\"slug\":\"eliska-valtrova\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"evaltrova@sonica-fitout.com\",\"71\":\"\",\"66\":\"As a Design Lead Client Executive, I am responsible for Sonica design tasks. My role involves dealing with Clients and understanding their needs as well as working with the Sonica Team to carry out every project from cradle to grave. My work demands strong creative flair with good technical knowledge and professional approach to deadlines and costs.\",\"70\":[\"173\"],\"65\":\"Design Lead Client Executive\",\"68\":\"I love working in fast-paced environment. I enjoy being free to develop and improve all kinds of design solutions as well as trying to meet Clients expectations and to see successfully completed projects handed back into Customer hands.\",\"67\":\"Sonica is one of the fastest growing and award winning fitout company on the current market with a great team to work with on every single project. Professional attitude and an open minded approach to reach the top in the fitout industry make Sonica stand out from the crowd.\"}}', '2018-02-15 17:58:26', '2018-02-15 17:58:26', '0c5f10e9-5f95-49b0-98d9-f09f5acef9d6'),
 ('120', '157', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Ray Argue\",\"slug\":\"ray-argue\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"rargue@sonica-fitout.com\",\"71\":\"\",\"66\":\"As Technical Services Manager it is my responsibility to coordinate the general and specialist services for each project. Due to Sonica\\u2019s diverse client base this can range from an office fit-out to Optics laboratories. Each new project brings its own challenge which is what keeps me going.\",\"70\":[\"189\"],\"65\":\"Technical Services Manager\",\"68\":\"For me it\\u2019s the project review, when we get into the detail of the design. Understanding the process flow of multi serviced designs and developing programs to delivery it on time and within budget. Integrating client direct specialist services and ensuring seamless cohesion to produce the clients once notional dream.\",\"67\":\"Sonica has been built from a solid base, by proven industry professionals. There is a drive in this company that carries you along wanting to deliver more, produce better and never stop expecting more.\"}}', '2018-02-15 17:58:37', '2018-02-15 17:58:37', '91012d5a-2966-4a0a-b5e2-aae10717cf3e'),
 ('121', '158', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"John Donnelly\",\"slug\":\"john-donnelly\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"jdonnelly@sonica-fitout.com\",\"71\":\"\",\"66\":\"As Site Manager, my role orientates around all aspects of the construction site from project planning and H&S to client liaison and quality control. Communication to all parties is vital.\",\"70\":[\"177\"],\"65\":\"Site Manager\",\"68\":\"I love seeing how all the different trades in construction work alongside each other and help to bring the architects drawing from concept to reality.\",\"67\":\"What has impressed me most about Sonica is the structured approach they take to run all their projects. They have a simple five step process which is custom built to every one of our clients. This project organisation is a pivotal reason why our clients keep coming back to us\"}}', '2018-02-15 17:58:48', '2018-02-15 17:58:48', '308306c0-3e3d-4c82-b826-9cc811a0fe7f'),
 ('122', '143', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Donnacha Neary\",\"slug\":\"donnacha-neary\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"dneary@sonica-fitout.com\",\"66\":\"As Managing Director, I\'m actively involved in everything that we do here at Sonica, leading the Team by example through dedication and commitment to exceeding our Client\'s expectations. I\'m a visible resource to our clients, equally at home walking the job sites as I am sitting in the Boardroom.\",\"70\":[\"169\"],\"65\":\"Managing Director\",\"68\":\"Motivating my guys, encouraging their development, celebrating their achievements and pushing them to be the very best they can be. The real excitement for me comes when I see how their hard work and dedication directly impacts the overall success of a project.\",\"67\":\"Our unwavering desire to continually improve our business, to strive to make your project our best project yet, means that in Sonica you have a firm of fitout experts dedicated to going far beyond what typically passes for Client service. It\'s that desire that makes Sonica a great place to work, and Sonica a great Team to work with.\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:00:44', '2018-02-15 18:00:44', '4ece0bb6-271e-4881-801c-6ed3370c3770'),
 ('123', '144', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Marie Halpenny\",\"slug\":\"marie-halpenny\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"mhalpenny@sonica-fitout.com\",\"66\":\"As Senior Surveyor and Commercial Manager, I am responsible for developing the surveying department and for the profitable management of all our projects from inception to completion.\",\"70\":[\"183\"],\"65\":\"Head of Surveying\",\"68\":\"The nature of the fit-out industry introduces us to new Clients and Design Team members every day. This diversity allows us to continuously develop new friendships and forge new working relations which makes every day different.\",\"67\":\"Clients should engage Sonica if they are looking for a recognised name in the industry, recognition that was earned as a result of hard work and forging good relations. We are a formidable team with vast cumulative experience in the fitout market - experience we are delighted to share with our Professional Teams and Clients.\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:01:13', '2018-02-15 18:01:13', '557d6f0c-2fee-43a4-b559-46801786bb33'),
 ('124', '102', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"21 Charlemont\",\"slug\":\"21-charlemont\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Rohan Holdings is a leader in the complex business of developing prestige offices, high quality business parks and industrial premises. With over 40 years\\u2019 experience in land acquisition, design, planning, construction and tenant fit out, Rohan Holdings have a respected proven track record of delivering projects on time, within budget and to their clients\\u2019 satisfaction.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Working in the shell of the newly completed 21 Charlemont Place Office Block, our brief was to take the \\u201cGrey Box\\u201d finish to full Landlord CAT-A standard to LEED Gold and A3 BER Rating.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Set against an aggressive time line driven by a signed single tenancy lease for the whole building, works included complete raised floor installation, soft floor finishes, partitions and ceilings, joinery and decorations. Our brief also extended the the complete M&E installations to include A\\/C, lighting, protective services, basement and roof plant, louvres & screening with full testing and commissioning.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Cat A Office Fitout<\\/li><li>Extensive Green Roof<\\/li><li>LEED Gold Certification and A3 BER<\\/li><li>Balconies and Feature Roof Terrace<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>3,420m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>2-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>10 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:07:50', '2018-02-15 18:07:50', '82d3e7b2-6c04-4bbd-85be-ebc3fbfa2206'),
 ('125', '103', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>We are delighted to showcase the successful completion of a new 15k sq.ft. Corporate HQ office in Dublin\\u2019s City Centre for a Private Sonica Client, the results of which are absolutely stunning.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our brief took the project from an existing Landlord CAT-A finish (which was fully stripped out) to their fitted out Corporate HQ in 8 weeks from commencement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were undertaken in a multi-tenanted office development with continual intensive daily co-ordination with the sitting Building Management Team. Added to the time sensitive nature of the project was the Client\\u2019s \\u201cnot-to-exceed\\u201d occupation date which was a key consideration in our aggressive construction programme.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the high degree of cellularisation to form the various offices, meeting spaces and executive boardrooms, the mechanical scope required considerable addition to the primary Landlord ventilation provisions via. intensive upgrades, modelling and building control integration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project scope also included a large specialist joinery component, extensive meeting spaces with feature exposed ceilings and feature lighting throughout, bespoke reception area, feature hard and soft floorings, substantial active IT solution, a fully redundant IT backbone install to main comms room, high-end Corporate level access control and security install, A\\/V delivery and a full furniture installation across the complete floor plate.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li><sub>Design and VE development to suit budget parameters<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>International collaboration with multiple project stakeholders<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Co-ordination with local Team on relocation deliverables<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Comms room commissioned and complete 2 weeks before handover to allow Client IT access.<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Live building environment<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Full M&E data & VC co-ordination<\\/sub><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 4\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,500m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>7 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:08:13', '2018-02-15 18:08:13', '32bfb8a7-7881-4b63-924d-61f8a386352f'),
 ('126', '104', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Demonware\",\"slug\":\"demonware\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Demonware are an Irish software development company specialising in creating networking software and services for computer game development, most notably for the Call of Duty on-line game franchise. The company were acquired by US game publisher Activision Blizzard in 2007 and have offices in Dublin, Vancouver and Shanghai.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the complexity of the works and the fact that the offices would remain LIVE through the refurbishment, the project was bid on a 2-stage basis with an open tender process to identify two preferred bidders followed by a post-tender interview process to select their final fitout partner. A large part of the Client Team\\u2019s decision making process also centered on input and commentary from the Contractor into the initial scheme design with recommendations on buildability and value engineering. We were suitably delighted to win out at interview stage and be appointed as Demonware\\u2019s contractor of choice \\u2013 with us on board, planning for their new European HQ officially kicked-off led by international architects, Urban Agency.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The scope of works included segregation of the existing floor plate into Live \\/ Under-Construction areas, the complete strip of the demised floor areas, full M&E, IT and A\\/V installation, a bespoke fabricated solution for Meeting Rooms (made from curved glass pods) and Team Huddle Rooms (machined birch faced plywood), full soft & hard flooring, extensive graphics package and the management & supervision of the Client\\u2019s furniture vendors. Of further note was the fact that the project was completed with the Client in full occupation on the 5th Floor of a multi-tenanted building.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The finished project is a fabulous addition to our portfolio of works and is a job that we are very proud to have been involved with.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full design realisation and co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Staff migration & move management<\\/li><li>Full M&E and IT installations<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package<\\/li><li>Curved glass huddle rooms<\\/li><li>Birch-faced plywood huddle pods<\\/li><li>Exposed building structure & ceiling<\\/li><li>Corporate signage & brand identity<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Parnell Street\\r\\nDublin1\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"I just want take a breath to let you know how happy we\'ve been so far with how the build is being managed by your Team and with the quality of the work that is being done. Harry, Doug and Ray have been a pleasure to work with throughout these past 14 weeks. What could have been a very stressful experience for us, has turned out to be an education in how a professional renovation should run. Thanks to you and your Team for this.\",\"62\":\"Amy Smith, Business Services Manager, Demonware\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,800m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>4-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>14 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:08:27', '2018-02-15 18:08:27', '096747cd-4332-4ac8-864d-de2ca076bbca'),
 ('127', '105', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Hubspot\",\"slug\":\"hubspot\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>We had the tremendous fortune to meet with and work alongside our friends in Hubspot when our MD PM\\u2019d their very first Dublin office for just 8-people five short years ago.&nbsp; Since then, we\\u2019ve had the distinct honour to be part of their expansion year-on-year as the Sonica Team continued to service their ever increasing head count and office space requirements.&nbsp; Their growth in Dublin has been simply astounding.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>It is therefore with great pride, and shared enthusiasm for their continued future successes, that we announce the completion and launch of their new EMEA HQ in Dublin, which was opened in March 2016 with substantial (and well deserved) fanfare across the Irish media.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We look forward to working with Hubspot as their PM of choice here in Dublin, and wish them every good fortune in their fabulous new home. #HubSpotDigsDublin<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full Design Realisation and Co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Landlord Approval and Grant of Licence to Alter<\\/li><li>Local Design Team Appointment & Management as Lead Consultant<\\/li><li>Complete Project Financial Control & Package Management<\\/li><li>Client Direct Vendor Engagement and Management<\\/li><li>Staff Migration & Move Management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 1\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Sonica has been a phenomenal partner to HubSpot - they always keep our interests front-and-centre and are beyond timely and thorough. If you wanted a partner that can do it all and give the attention these complex fitout projects command, it is Sonica Fitout - they simply get it, and get results.\",\"62\":\"Ken Papa, Facilities Director, Hubspot Inc.\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>2,750m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>12 weeks Design Co-ordination, Contract Formulation & Lease Management<\\/li><li>10 weeks Build Management On-Site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:08:46', '2018-02-15 18:08:46', '879b7497-dc34-4b1c-88f7-ccb5b62dae43'),
 ('128', '106', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client-1\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Our brief was to strip and refit the old Anglo Irish Bank space over two floors in St. Stephen\\u2019s Green House and transform it into an expansive, sophisticated, tech-savvy office for our Client\\u2019s expanded new HQ in Ireland.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were executed on a 10-week programme within a fully engaged, heavily trafficked, multi-tenanted building. With it\\u2019s location in the heart of Dublin\\u2019s shopping district on the iconic St. Stephen\\u2019s Green, the delivery of the finished project on an accelerated timeline formed a hugely important part of our project execution plan where the delivery \\/ collection logistics, overall traffic management, DCC liaison, out of hours works scheduling and compliance with strict building noise restrictions all required in-depth consideration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Architectural Design included a substantial joinery package, multiple floor finishes, open grid exposed ceilings, extensive Client direct vend supervision and migration management. Other packages included substantial upgrades to the Mechanical, Electrical, IT and AV installations with all service works demanding a high level of co-ordinated attention to guarantee that the vision for the completed space was realised.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Large open plan spaces with extensive perimeter cellularisation.<\\/li><li>Extensive M&E & IT package with \\u201copen grid\\u201d M&E ceiling services<\\/li><li>Engagement of specialist contractors to facilitate works in a time restricted programme.<\\/li><li>Co-ordination with local teams and stakeholders on relocation deliverables.<\\/li><li>Cost and VE development to suit strict budget parameters.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>3,000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>10 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:08:54', '2018-02-15 18:08:54', 'f5e6a0d7-9b54-4f4e-9fac-f22d6f6b188d'),
 ('129', '107', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"UDG Healthcare\",\"slug\":\"udg-healthcare\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Designed by RKD Interiors, our brief took the assignment from an Existing Landlord CAT-A area over 2-separate tenancies, both of which were then fully stripped back to basic shell and core structure as part of our works, to become UDG Healthcare\\u2019s Corporate HQ within a 10-week period from Commencement on site.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were performed unobtrusively within a fully engaged, highly trafficked, multi-tenanted building with close overlap to Campus Management, Client Stakeholders and neighbouring tenants.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Packages encompassed a sizeable stylish joinery element and complex Mechanical, Electrical & IT upgrades to service the open-plan work-space areas and segmental modular offices & meeting rooms. The main Reception features an inviting design element luring to a quirky \\u2018Breakout Area Canteen\\u2019 with feature brick internal facades, critall glazed screens, floating \\u2018wooden\\u2019 acoustic ceilings and matchless tiled flooring.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the nature and scale of the sharp trapezoidal shaped walls and ceilings, paired with the diverging display of flooring and wall colours, the detailing in the Architectural packages required a Sonica level of attention to guarantee that the Architects vision for the completed space was realised.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Design and VE development to suit strict budget parameters<\\/li><li>Comms room commissioned and complete 3 weeks before handover to allow Client IT access<\\/li><li>Liaison and management of Client Direct vendors<\\/li><li>Project acceleration to ensure no client \\u2018down-time\\u2019 and smooth, quick turn-around on staff migrations<\\/li><li>Co-ordination with local Team on relocation deliverables<\\/li><li>M&E and IT upgrades throughout<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Citywest Business Campus\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"It was great to work with Hugh Ward and his team at Sonica Fitout on our new HQ in Riverwalk, Citywest. We were very impressed with the level of professionalism and attention to detail on every aspect of this project which produced a high standard of finish. Sonica Fitouts commitment to this project ensured that it came in on programme and within budget. Everyone is delighted with the final result.\",\"62\":\"Donal Burke, Head of Procurement\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,250m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-Con<\\/li><li>10 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:09:06', '2018-02-15 18:09:06', '10f800c3-8265-4ec8-ad8a-cddfa4389e76'),
 ('130', '108', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"3 Arena\",\"slug\":\"3-arena\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Full D&B project from receipt of Client outline brief to final delivery and handover. Development of a central defined theme to roll out across the complete rebrand project was the key deliverable.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>1672 individual ceiling suspended \\u201cCities\\u201d in the 4th floor bar, over 2,400 individually controlled LED lights per City (and that\\u2019s just one area on one floor..!)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3m dia. \\u201cOculus\\u201d video back-projected onto VIP ceiling \\u2013 video specifically commissioned for the Kaleidoscope Bar fitout.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fully programmable KNX Lighting system with user defined colour and dimming set points depending on event and scene setting requirements. This linked back to main venue DALI system for central control by Venue management.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fully interactive Twitter feed linked to feature \\u201cfloating Megalopolis\\u201d to allow visitors Tweet their venue experiences directly into the bars in real time.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Conceptual development and full project design<\\/li><li>GMP Contract Sum<\\/li><li>Intricate project programming<\\/li><li>Live venue interaction & co-ordination<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"North Wall Quay, Dublin 1\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Have to say it looks absolutely incredible. Proud to have worked on such a prestigious project for such a prestigious company as\\r\\nSonica Fitout. From all at Devlin in Design. Congratulations to Sonica.\",\"62\":\"Enda Devlin, Devlin in Design\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>4000m2 overall Venue Area.<\\/li><li>Works spread across three separate project sites running concurrently.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>8 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:09:27', '2018-02-15 18:09:27', 'c10ef339-2778-4bea-aa9d-e7800c9593dc'),
 ('131', '109', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Salesforce\",\"slug\":\"salesforce\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Salesforce&nbsp;is the world\\u2019s leading CRM software and enterprise cloud ecosystem, their \\u201cCustomer Success Platform\\u201d helps businesses grow into a more streamlined, effective and efficient organisations across sales, service, marketing and more.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Sonica Ops Team has had the pleasure of being part of SFDC\\u2019s expansion by servicing their ever increasing head count and office space requirements for the past 3-years.&nbsp; It is therefore with great pride that we showcase the latest SFDC office completion, a 15,000 sq.ft. floor plate in Central Park.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works involved the demolition and strip out of the previous tenant\\u2019s existing fitted offices to cater for the new Salesforce remodelled floor plate layout.&nbsp; The office design placed emphasis on increased Team collaboration with all new open plan workstations, meeting rooms, offices, boardrooms, flexible spaces, staff kitchens & canteen areas, breakout areas and a number of bespoke \\u201cTechForce Bars\\u201d all part of the required brief.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>They have since been voted Ireland\\u2019s Best Workplace \\u2013 the company was ranked No. 1 on the list of the Best Large Places to Work, a ranking based on employees\\u2019 own assessments of their experiences.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Full GMP Build Delivery<\\/li><li>Extensive Feature Joinery Package procurement<\\/li><li>Complete staff auditorium with extensive A\\/V<\\/li><li>Client Direct Vendor Engagement and Management<\\/li><li>Staff Migration & Move Management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Central Park, Dublin 18\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Just a little note to say a BIG thank you to you and all the Sonica team. It was a real pleasure working with you all. Thanks for your guidance, assistance and patience! Fingers crossed for the next one.\",\"62\":\"Cathy Mooney, Senior Office Manager\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1500m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>10 weeks Design Co-ordination, Procurement, GMP Formulation<\\/li><li>12 weeks Build Management On-Site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:09:38', '2018-02-15 18:09:38', 'b5dbe6f7-4250-4641-8032-2f6e5d7ae3f5'),
 ('132', '110', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Wipro\",\"slug\":\"wipro\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Since entering the Irish market in 2015, WIPRO have gone from strength to strength securing substantial projects for their ever increasing Client base. This success has been met with a rapid increase in head count and exponential office space requirement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Having already completed over 50k sq.ft. of office space in Dublin for WIPRO since 2015, we were delighted to build upon and advance the great working relationship we had developed with both their International and Local Teams when they appointed us again as their Turnkey D&B Fitout Specialist for their new expansion offices in Ballsbridge.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were undertaken in a multi-tenanted office development with continual intensive daily co-ordination with the sitting Campus Management Team. Added to the time sensitive nature of the project was the Client\\u2019s \\u201cnot-to-exceed\\u201d occupation date which was a key consideration in our aggressive construction programme.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the high degree of cellularisation to form the various offices, meeting spaces, VC Rooms & Executive Boardrooms, the mechanical scope required considerable addition to the primary Landlord ventilation provisions via. intensive upgrades, modelling and building control integration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project scope also included a large specialist joinery component, exposed ceilings and feature lighting throughout, feature hard and soft floorings, substantial active IT solution, a fully redundant IT backbone install with UPS back up to main comms room, high-end Corporate level access control and security install, A\\/V delivery and a full furniture installation across the complete floor plate.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full Design Realisation and Co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Landlord Approval and Grant of Licence to Alter<\\/li><li>Local Design Team Appointment & Management as Lead Consultant<\\/li><li>Complete Project Financial Control & Package Management<\\/li><li>Client Direct Vendor Engagement and Management<\\/li><li>Staff Migration & Move Management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Ballsbridge\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>8 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:09:46', '2018-02-15 18:09:46', 'a76e2e5e-710f-4377-9765-b04f30bb88b6'),
 ('133', '111', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client-2\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Sonica Fitout were contracted to completely refurbish the Ground Floor lobby of the headquarters of one of Ireland\\u2019s leading providers of wealth management and financial advisory services. Clients of this prestigious private client are used to a meticulous attention to detail and as such this was reflected in the design and level of finish expected.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The intent was to provide enclosed, private areas throughout the space with which to hold impromptu, private meetings while maintaining a bright, open and modern feel throughout. Combined with the extremely well-appointed joinery package the overall feel of the space was one of practical opulence and luxury.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The scope of works was a complete refurbishment with curved recessed bulkheads all LED backlit, stone tiling throughout, new security gates and curved glazed meeting rooms all surrounding the walnut clad lift core that integrated seamlessly with an oversized reception desk. In addition new bathroom and kitchen facilities were completed as well as all new air conditioning throughout the floor.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Following a week\\u2019s pre construction this project was delivered in 5 weeks over multiple phases keeping live access available to staff members 24 hours a day 7 days a week with minimal disruption.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Natural Stone floor<\\/li><li>Bespoke Walnut wall cladding<\\/li><li>Curved glazed partitions throughout<\\/li><li>Oversized feature reception desk<\\/li><li>Backlit feature ceilings throughout<\\/li><li>New staff \\u201cspeedlanes\\u201d<\\/li><li>New facilities<\\/li><li>Completely revamped AC system.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>Reception areas<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-Con<\\/li><li>5 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:09:56', '2018-02-15 18:09:56', 'df25cc3b-e80e-48a0-b9a8-f170f4fc1c8d'),
 ('134', '112', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"SAS\",\"slug\":\"sas\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>SAS is a global market leader in business analytics software and services and is listed as being in the Top-100 Best Companies to work for worldwide. We were delighted to complete their prestigious new 1,300m2 HQ office in Dublin\\u2019s IFSC complex.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were undertaken in a multi-tenanted, fully occupied building with extensive noise restriction in place to avoid disruption to other businesses on-site.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The scope included complete demolitions of the existing floor plate with subsequent re-fit of partitions, glazing, managers offices, corporate meeting rooms, multiple floor finishes, decorations and a bespoke branding and graphics package. The brief also extended to the supply & installation of all new operator workstations, cellular office stations and boardroom furniture with completion of all M&E, IT and A\\/V services.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The completed project truly reflects SAS\\u2019s strong corporate identity through the entire space and we were delighted to hand over the finished article to the Client\\u2019s exacting standards and expectations.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Fully occupied Building Environment<\\/li><li>Management of Client Direct Vend Packages<\\/li><li>Complete M&E, IT and A\\/V service installations<\\/li><li>Corporate Brand Package co-ordination & implementation<\\/li><li>Extensive corporate office cellularisation<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"La Touche House IFSC, Dublin 1\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"I can highly recommend Sonica Fit Out, their professionalism and flexible approach in challenging circumstances resulted in a smooth and timely delivery of SAS project, the entire team were a pleasure to work with.\",\"62\":\"Karen Chisman, Head of Corporate Services at SAS\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,300m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>8 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:10:08', '2018-02-15 18:10:08', 'c9fddbf5-a839-477c-8893-99ae1b6ac780'),
 ('135', '113', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Calvin Klein\",\"slug\":\"calvin-klein\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Calvin Klein is one of the leading fashion design and marketing studios in the world. They are a global lifestyle brand that exemplifies bold, progressive ideals and a seductive, and often minimal, aesthetic. After nearly 50 years of trading, Calvin Klein continues to be a cultural catalyst across the globe today.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We were delighted to be selected by Calvin Klein to carry out the complete relocation and fitout of their new flagship stores (CK Jeans & CK Underwear) in Irelands Premier Shopping destination, Kildare Village. Our brief was to create a completed space that combines the retail experience with the architectural aesthetic of this refined fashion collection.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were undertaken concurrently in both stores and included the full strip out of the existing premises with subsequent re-installation of new partitions and floor finishes, complete M&E & IT rework, co-ordination of a bespoke high-end joinery package and management of the internal and external CK signage install. In addition, the relocation to a temporary \\u201cGo Live\\u201d space while our refurbishment works were progressing (as well as relocation back to stores upon completion) also formed part of our project brief.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The finished product succeeds in promoting the Calvin Klein identity within Kildare Village and provides a top of the range retail experience for shoppers within both stores.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Extensive feature joinery package<\\/li><li>Bespoke feature lighting installation<\\/li><li>Full move management<\\/li><li>Extensive floor finishes<\\/li><li>POS selection, install and commisisoning<\\/li><li>Construction of all fixed merchandise and sales displays<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Kildare Village\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Our goal is always to create a space that combines the retail experience with the architectural aesthetic our fashion collection represents. We had the tremendous pleasure to collaborate with Sonica Fitout to accomplish this in our new Kildare Village stores - the finished results speak entirely for themselves.\",\"62\":\"Antonios Krantidis, CK Project Manager\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>400m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>5 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:10:17', '2018-02-15 18:10:17', '641de288-8be2-40fd-a935-31dfe06521ba'),
 ('136', '114', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"100 Stephen\\u2019s Green\",\"slug\":\"100-stephens-green\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>100 St. Stephen\\u2019s Green, a red brick Georgian located in the iconic South West corner of the Green, was originally sub-divided into six dated apartments. Sonica were engaged by property owners DAVY to develop the building into a prestigious single tenancy office above a 1 bedroom apartment in the basement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The nature of the premises, and it\\u2019s status as a listed building, meant the project had to be handled with the utmost care. Working hand-in-hand with Neasa Donnellan Architects and Dublin City Council, each element of the build was scrutinised for compliance of FSC, DAC, heritage protection and quality.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The work scope included full glazing replacement with all new sliding sash windows with slimlite double glazed panels in keeping with the original, full facade restoration and re-pointing, roof replacement, extensive structural works, removal of the existing basement slab and replacement with complete tanking system and new drainage and fire protection to existing staircore as per current regulations.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Internally the high-end office interiors include full power and data cabling and floor boxes throughout, bespoke joinery and panelling in every space, restored original Georgian features on all floors, newly landscaped rear yard, high quality floor finishes and a luxury, own door, 1-bed 2-bath self contained apartment in the basement.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Protected Georgian structure<\\/li><\\/ul>Hardwood sash windows with Slimlite glazing<br>Facade and roof restoration<br>Full internal strip out<br>Data cabling throughout to central rack location<br>New gas fired rad heating system<br>Hand made crown mouldings from sample of original<br>Period correct feature joinery throughout<br>Protection and restoration of existing Georgian features<br>Luxury floor finishes<br>Self contained apartment\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"With Sonica at the helm, the project ran seamlessly on-site - any unforeseen events were dealt with quickly and programme was never compromised. We were very impressed with the quality of their finishes and found the whole Company to be very well organised and efficient. We would be very happy to work with them again.\",\"62\":\"Neasa Donnellan\\r\\nProject Architect\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>350m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>18 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:10:34', '2018-02-15 18:10:34', '98ce0d62-7a0d-4e36-a1f8-a3cdb959ff18'),
 ('137', '115', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"City North Hotel\",\"slug\":\"city-north-hotel\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>The City North Hotel & Conference Centre is a prestigious 4-Star Hotel located 30-mins North of Dublin City Center which offers luxury accommodation and an exquisite Ballroom for Conferences, Events and Weddings.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As part of the Hotel\\u2019s recent redevelopment, we were appointed to manage the extensive restructure of all of their main front of house Client facing spaces comprising of a new warm and welcoming Reception area, a fully refitted Hotel Bar and Lounge area, a Restaurant and an exclusive new Conference & Ballroom facility.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were carried out in a live working environment (the hotel remained fully functional during the refit) and was divided into multiple phases to ensure minimal restriction & disruption to guests during construction. All phases included substantial demolition works, full M&E installations, new partitions and feature ceilings, bespoke lighting with textured high-end joinery and exquisite segmented hardwood flooring.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the nature of the works, the project required extensive management of multiple on-site trades and was completed against an aggressive programme to coincide with media published announcements on the rebrand and official launch date.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>High-end joinery package<\\/li><li>Exquisite segmented flooring<\\/li><li>Management of multiple trades<\\/li><li>Project multi-phasing<\\/li><li>Full M&E installation<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"M1 Corridor, North Co. Dublin\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,500m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1 Week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>12 Weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:10:43', '2018-02-15 18:10:43', '81b0c511-dc17-4ffc-8f91-02c50721a4b9'),
 ('138', '116', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"RKD Interiors\",\"slug\":\"rkd-interiors\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>RKD Interiors is a market leading interior architecture firm based in Dublin. The team, led by Justin Treacy, consists of the very best in creative Architects and Interior Designers who work collaboratively with the in-house support team of Designers, Technicians & CAD \\/ BIM Coordinators and the wider resource and expertise of RKD Architects. At the core of their philosophy is a practical and pragmatic approach to delivering the best environments for the most appropriate capital outlay. Having worked with RKD Interiors on numerous occasions in the past, we were aware of the exacting standards that were expected from the outset on this collaboration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project was pitched as a real shop window fitout to showcase RKD\\u2019s standard and design capability to prospective visiting RKD Clients and we approached the project like any other: to deliver best in market product with zero defects at handover. Covering 6,000 sq ft over 3 floors, the work scope comprised of inspirational studios to the 1st and 2nd floors, with areas designated for collaboration and huddle meetings allowing the designers to get creative with a bespoke staff caf\\u00e9, meeting rooms and social spaces based on the Ground Floor.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The overall brief was to produce a comfortable, modern and above all functional workspace with a professional design that exceeds expectations even in an area such as Baggot St. where high end eateries and businesses are the norm. One of the key features, as part of RKD interiors on-going commitment to a greener work environment, was to provide ample, secure bike storage for staff. Not only has this been achieved but it has also become a real design focal point, which upon entry sets a modern and progressive tone. Other features include the herringbone flooring which seamlessly combines durability with design, the increasingly popular crittal glazing and bespoke joinery throughout. In addition, you will find numerous design touches, as you would expect of an RKD interiors design, such as the exposed swag cabling to the lights in the cafe to give the illusion of extra height, the plywood routered RKD logo at entry with integrated shelving and the comfortable lounge located midway through the ground floor.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project was delivered in 5 weeks following a 1-week pre-construction and mobilisation period.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Bespoke feature joinery and glazed partition packages<\\/li><li>Numerous floor finishes running seamlessly throughout<\\/li><li>Staff \\u201cCafe\\u201d<\\/li><li>Internal, secure bike park<\\/li><li>2 floors of bright, modern studio space<\\/li><li>M&E and IT upgrades throughout<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Ballsbridge, Dublin 4\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Working with Sonica was a great experience. We would like to thank the team for delivering for such demanding taskmasters, for working with us to realise and achieve our design in a very tight timeframe, and for making the whole delivery process a thoroughly enjoyable and fun experience for us all.\",\"62\":\"Liat Greenhot, RKD Interiors\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>600m2 over 3 floors<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week pre-construction<\\/li><li>5 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:10:52', '2018-02-15 18:10:52', 'd1e91248-bedf-4492-90b6-03aed5314be0'),
 ('139', '117', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Fitter Faster Stronger\",\"slug\":\"fitter-faster-stronger\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Established only 3-years ago, Fitter Faster Stronger (FFS)&nbsp;is now one of the leading specialist facilities in Dublin providing personal one-on-one or group training&nbsp;across a range of classes and exercise types, from total body strength to full metabolic conditioning.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Having successfully completed FFS\\u2019s original gym refurbishment in 2016, and due to their phenomenal expansion and growth, we were delighted to be appointed by the Management Team in FFS to develop and complete their 2nd bespoke premises inside of 18-months.&nbsp; Working with Courtney McDonnell Design, we were delighted to take on the brief of creating a new space which motivates, engages and pushes personal goals to the highest level whilst also realising the strong branding the FFS model carries.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The space is divided into three main parts \\u2013 the gym, utility space and break & members areas. &nbsp;Works included the strip out & demolitions of the entire old premises followed by full M&E installation (to include a DMX programmable lighting system defined by gym instructors to suit mood or event), bespoke feature flooring across&nbsp;different surfaces, extensive landscaping works at the rear gardens to become an outdoor training area, complete joinery co-ordination of utility space and members area and a personalised graphics package to enhance the members workouts and provide guidance through the whole space.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Complete strip out of all incumbent areas<\\/li><li>Full M&E installation with programmable DMX ambiance lighting<\\/li><li>Bespoke feature flooring<\\/li><li>Extensive landscaping works to external gym area<\\/li><li>D&B joinery & upholstery package<\\/li><li>Graphics co-ord and installation<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Leeson Street\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"The level of professionalism and proficiency on the first project we carried out with Sonica Fitout really impressed us, hence the reason why we went back to them for our 2nd premises. The entire fitout was completed on an aggressive timeline with multiple moving parts, but the team here at FFS are once again delighted with the finished product that was achieved, it looks awesome!\",\"62\":\"Rory McInerney, Managing Director, FFS\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>Complete Basement to Georgian Building, Lesson St.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>6 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:03', '2018-02-15 18:11:03', '23c88f17-81f4-429b-a1a3-f31a84aecf7e'),
 ('140', '118', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client-3\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Sonica Fitout was appointed by CBRE to act as Main Contractor for the refurbishment and upgrade of this 5th floor Corporate office space located at East Point Business Park in Dublin.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Client\\u2019s fitout requirements were driven by an internal review to develop new ways of working. The challenge was to take these findings and ideas and bring them into a layout scheme that realised all their requirements whilst also increasing headcount within the floor space. Our project brief then consisted of the demolition and re-build of the existing layouts, installation of new branded specialist joinery items throughout the floor, a vibrant colour theming and graphics package co-ordination, installation of new glazed partitions including folding walls with modifications to the existing data infrastructure and the mechanical and electrical services of the space.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The completed office space now promotes the Client\\u2019s identity and provides a new fresh working space for staff.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Extensive Feature Joinery Package<\\/li><li>Data Infrastructure Installation<\\/li><li>M&E Services Modification<\\/li><li>Numerous Floor Finishes running seamlessly throughout<\\/li><li>Corporate Signage & Brand Identity<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"East Point Business Park, Dublin 3\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,500m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>2-week Pre-Construction<\\/li><li>5 weeks Build Management On-Site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:10', '2018-02-15 18:11:10', '472388bf-5d94-40d5-9110-ebc0a7b5833a'),
 ('141', '119', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"M & S Simply Food\",\"slug\":\"m-s-simply-food\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>M&S Simply Food are an off-shoot of the famous high street British multinational specialising on high quality grab-and-go ready meal ranges and every day food selections.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This project consisted of the fitout from shell and core of the new M&S Simply Food outlet in Dublin\\u2019s Heuston Train Station. Works revolved around the installation of new M&E services, flooring, internal partitions, decorations, PoS counters, feature joinery, product refrigeration, the co-ordination of Client direct vendors and the installation of internal and external corporate graphics.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A carefully considered site management & works execution plan was key to the success of the project with close co-ordination with Station management while works progressed in the busy station.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>New M&E services installation<\\/li><li>Feature joinery package<\\/li><li>M&S corporate graphics install<\\/li><li>Exposed ceilings throughout<\\/li><li>LIVE station working environment<\\/li><li>Client Direct vendor management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 8\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Just a quick note to compliment and acknowledge the efforts of your Team on the Heuston Station M&S project. These types of projects are not simple, particularly from a co-ordination view point, but your Team demonstrated professionalism and proactive thinking in dealing with any issue that arose and delivered the project on programme. It has been great working with you right through the project and we look forward to working with Sonica again in the future.\",\"62\":\"Stephen Crean, Linesight PM\",\"58\":\"<p>200m2<\\/p>\",\"59\":\"<p>1-week Pre-construction<br>5 weeks on-site<\\/p>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:14', '2018-02-15 18:11:14', '43cd2b0a-3de2-405f-abdf-300c3033a197'),
 ('142', '119', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"M & S Simply Food\",\"slug\":\"m-s-simply-food\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>M&S Simply Food are an off-shoot of the famous high street British multinational specialising on high quality grab-and-go ready meal ranges and every day food selections.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This project consisted of the fitout from shell and core of the new M&S Simply Food outlet in Dublin\\u2019s Heuston Train Station. Works revolved around the installation of new M&E services, flooring, internal partitions, decorations, PoS counters, feature joinery, product refrigeration, the co-ordination of Client direct vendors and the installation of internal and external corporate graphics.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A carefully considered site management & works execution plan was key to the success of the project with close co-ordination with Station management while works progressed in the busy station.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>New M&E services installation<\\/li><li>Feature joinery package<\\/li><li>M&S corporate graphics install<\\/li><li>Exposed ceilings throughout<\\/li><li>LIVE station working environment<\\/li><li>Client Direct vendor management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dublin 8\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Just a quick note to compliment and acknowledge the efforts of your Team on the Heuston Station M&S project. These types of projects are not simple, particularly from a co-ordination view point, but your Team demonstrated professionalism and proactive thinking in dealing with any issue that arose and delivered the project on programme. It has been great working with you right through the project and we look forward to working with Sonica again in the future.\",\"62\":\"Stephen Crean, Linesight PM\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>200m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>5 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:21', '2018-02-15 18:11:21', 'f20eb9da-0e1d-4bfb-9a68-071623b5b755'),
 ('143', '120', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Wipro\",\"slug\":\"wipro-1\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Since entering the Irish market in 2015, WIPRO have gone from strength to strength securing substantial projects for their ever increasing Client base. This success has been met with a rapid increase in head count and exponential office space requirement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Having just completed their initial 30k sq.ft. office in Dublin\\u2019s Elm Park in 2015, we were delighted to build upon and advance the great working relationship we had developed with both their International and Local Teams when they appointed us again as their Turnkey D&B Fitout Specialist for their new expansion offices in Ballsbridge.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The brief was to capture the look and feel of what we had been previously delivered for them on the Elm Park project, but to take that blue print and move it on to the next level again \\u2013 no easy task if you were to look at the completed space in Elm Park!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>At 20k sq.ft. and running concurrently over two floors, works were undertaken in a multi-tenanted office development with continual intensive daily co-ordination with the sitting Campus Management Team. Added to the time sensitive nature of the project was the Client\\u2019s \\u201cnot-to-exceed\\u201d occupation date which was a key consideration in our aggressive construction programme.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the high degree of cellularisation to form the various offices, meeting spaces, VC Rooms & Executive Boardrooms, the mechanical scope required considerable addition to the primary Landlord ventilation provisions via. intensive upgrades, modelling and building control integration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project scope also included a large specialist joinery component, an extensive canteen space with exposed ceilings and feature lighting throughout, bespoke reception area, feature hard and soft floorings, substantial active IT solution, a fully redundant IT backbone install with UPS back up to main comms room, high-end Corporate level access control and security install, A\\/V delivery and a full furniture installation across the complete dual floor plate.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We wish Wipro continued success in their newest home and look forward to representing them again in their next round of expansions.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full Design Realisation and Co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Landlord Approval and Grant of Licence to Alter<\\/li><li>Local Design Team Appointment & Management as Lead Consultant<\\/li><li>Complete Project Financial Control & Package Management<\\/li><li>Client Direct Vendor Engagement and Management<\\/li><li>Staff Migration & Move Management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Ballsbridge\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"The bittersweet time has come to say thank you and farewell (albeit for now!) to the formidable & fantastic team that is Sonica. We can\\u2019t thank you enough for your dedication, enthusiasm and flexibility over the last year. We have worked together through different time zones, deadlines and (at times!) style preferences to ultimately create two unique Office environments which epitomise the Spirit of Wipro.\\r\\n\\r\\nThanks for sharing your vision with us and for the friendship that we\\u2019ve formed.\",\"62\":\"Trish Buckley, Admin. Manager, WIPRO Europe\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>2,000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>6 weeks design<\\/li><li>4 weeks pre-con<\\/li><li>10 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:32', '2018-02-15 18:11:32', 'd0363b4e-f8ab-4e32-b5c9-1d6074887384'),
 ('144', '121', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Anya Hindmarch\",\"slug\":\"anya-hindmarch\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p><em><\\/em>Founded in 1987, Anya Hindmarch has grown into a global brand with more than 45 stores including flagship outlets in New York, London, Tokyo and LA. Known for blending wit and creativity with the finest craftsmanship and innovative leatherwork techniques, they are stocked in many of the world\\u2019s best retail stores, from Barney\\u2019s in New York to BoonTheShop in Korea.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Following receipt of our outline brief, we were appointed to create a unique, bespoke new store for the brand in Kildare Village coupled with the strip out, surrender and relocation of the existing store within the campus. The new store was a complete turn key fitout from \\u201cgrey box\\u201d to open for business. The works comprised of new flooring details, changing room marketing and sales displays and complete joinery coordination as well as mechanical and electrical installation.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The completed project reflects Anya Hindmarch\\u2019s extraordinary identity with strong emphasis on minimalistic detail and a high level of finishes throughout.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Extensive feature joinery package<\\/li><li>Stunning solid oak herringbone flooring<\\/li><li>Bespoke glazed partition solution<\\/li><li>M&E and IT upgrades throughout<\\/li><li>Live Building working environment<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package and Client migration<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Kildare Village\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<p>100m2<\\/p>\",\"59\":\"<p>1-week pre-construction<br>8 weeks on-site<\\/p>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:39', '2018-02-15 18:11:39', '725c6db8-0877-486c-8c58-147599ed15ac'),
 ('145', '121', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Anya Hindmarch\",\"slug\":\"anya-hindmarch\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Founded in 1987, Anya Hindmarch has grown into a global brand with more than 45 stores including flagship outlets in New York, London, Tokyo and LA. Known for blending wit and creativity with the finest craftsmanship and innovative leatherwork techniques, they are stocked in many of the world\\u2019s best retail stores, from Barney\\u2019s in New York to BoonTheShop in Korea.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Following receipt of our outline brief, we were appointed to create a unique, bespoke new store for the brand in Kildare Village coupled with the strip out, surrender and relocation of the existing store within the campus. The new store was a complete turn key fitout from \\u201cgrey box\\u201d to open for business. The works comprised of new flooring details, changing room marketing and sales displays and complete joinery coordination as well as mechanical and electrical installation.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The completed project reflects Anya Hindmarch\\u2019s extraordinary identity with strong emphasis on minimalistic detail and a high level of finishes throughout.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Extensive feature joinery package<\\/li><li>Stunning solid oak herringbone flooring<\\/li><li>Bespoke glazed partition solution<\\/li><li>M&E and IT upgrades throughout<\\/li><li>Live Building working environment<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package and Client migration<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Kildare Village\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>100m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week pre-construction<\\/li><li>8 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:46', '2018-02-15 18:11:46', '5bd67acd-6bc9-4b91-96c2-5c832ddfd6d1'),
 ('146', '122', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client-4\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>We are delighted to showcase the successful completion of a new 30k sq.ft. Corporate HQ office in Dublin\\u2019s Citywest Business Campus for a Private Sonica Client, the results of which are absolutely stunning.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our brief took the project from an existing Landlord CAT-A finish (which was fully stripped out) to their fitted out Corporate HQ in 14 weeks from appointment.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were undertaken in a multi-tenanted office development with continual intensive daily co-ordination with the sitting Campus Management Team. Added to the time sensitive nature of the project was the Client\\u2019s \\u201cnot-to-exceed\\u201d occupation date which was a key consideration in our aggressive construction programme.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the high degree of cellularisation to form the various offices, meeting spaces and executive boardrooms, the mechanical scope required considerable addition to the primary Landlord ventilation provisions via. intensive upgrades, modelling and building control integration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project scope also included a large specialist joinery component, an extensive \\u201cTown Hall\\u201d meeting space with feature exposed ceilings and feature lighting throughout, bespoke reception area, feature hard and soft floorings, substantial active IT solution, a fully redundant IT backbone install with UPS back up to main comms room, gymnasium installation, high-end Corporate level access control and security install, A\\/V delivery and a full furniture installation across the complete floor plate.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Design and VE development to suit budget parameters<\\/li><li>International collaboration with multiple project stakeholders<\\/li><li>Co-ordination with local Team on relocation deliverables<\\/li><li>Comms room commissioned and complete 2 weeks before handover to allow Client IT access.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Citywest\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>3,000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>4 weeks pre-construction<\\/li><li>10 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:11:54', '2018-02-15 18:11:54', '114dd202-5e14-4785-b924-b2bfbd7c8c0e'),
 ('147', '123', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"AIG\",\"slug\":\"aig\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>AIG Europe Limited is a provider of innovative products and services, including car, property, travel, health and identity theft insurance products to more than half of the country\\u2019s top 100 companies as well as many public and private sector organisations and tens of thousands of individuals. They are also the proud main sponsor of the Dublin GAA Team #BackingEveryStep<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Working in their Irish HQ offices in the IFSC, our brief comprised of the removal and replacement of the complete existing building ventilation system followed by retro-install of a new AC system with associated architectural and electrical works. The brief also included a full upgrade of all WCs throughout the building, installation of new mechanical chilling plant at roof level, a fixed line system for roof access, Landlord common area refurbishment and a complete re-design and fitout of the 3rd Floor office space. All works were conducted within a live, fully occupied building environment.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The new office design placed emphasis on increased Team collaboration with all new open plan workstations, meeting rooms, offices, boardrooms, flexible spaces, staff kitchens & canteen areas, breakout areas and a number of bespoke \\u201cTech Bars\\u201d all part of the required brief.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Effective use of space was an issue in the previous office so the new office was designed with ample storage capabilities to reduce clutter. The overall look and feel of the completed offices are fresh, professional and welcoming with spectacular views across Dublin city.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The whole project was completed within the agreed tender time frame of 22 weeks.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Variety of work settings and collaboration spaces<\\/li><li>Extensive M&E Remodel & Upgrade<\\/li><li>High quality joinery<\\/li><li>Works in fully occupied building over 5-floor plates<\\/li><li>Management of Client Direct vendors into master programme of works<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"IFSC, Dublin\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"On behalf of the PM team, I would like to convey our thanks to the Sonica team for a job well done. A special word of thanks to your Construction Manager, Ray McCaul, for his 100% commitment in achieving PC. This was a challenging project on a number of fronts and this achievement is not to be underestimated.\",\"62\":\"Allan Murphy, Director, Scott-Murphy. Client PM\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>8,000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>22 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:14:09', '2018-02-15 18:14:09', '6372c988-d4bc-4970-9819-d927d19dca38');
