 ('162', '136', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Axway\",\"slug\":\"axway\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Over 11,000 Companies Worldwide rely on AXWAY for their B2B software solutions. Axway relied on just one, Sonica Fitout, for their new Dublin HQ office fitout.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sonica appointed the Architectural and M&E Design Teams and also acted as traditional Main Contractor for the fitout with responsibility for overall design verification and certification of the M&E systems.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works involved the full strip out of the existing floor plate in preparation for the formation of open plan offices, manager cellular offices, boardroom facilities with full A\\/V capability, new staff canteen, comms room, bathrooms & staff shower rooms.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sonica also engaged a Graphic Design company to develop wall art and murals throughout the office space that reflected the Company\\u2019s vision and message.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were conducted on the 1st floor of Investment House in Dublin, a multi tenanted fully occupied Live office block, with all logistics for these operations managed by the Sonica Site Team.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Full bathroom and shower room installations<\\/li><li>Extensive Graphics and Wall Art Design<\\/li><li>Lead role in Design verification and certification<\\/li><li>Aggressive programme delivered in a fully occupied multi-tennanted environment<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Pembroke Street Upper, Dublin\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"To invest our time best in on our role as Client Representatives, we need a Contractor that makes the successful completion of the project their main and only focus. We get that every time we work with Sonica - it makes the whole process a pleasure for all concerned.\",\"62\":\"Andrew McCracken, Director, Jones Lang LaSalle\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1200m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>8 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:16:34', '2018-02-15 18:16:34', '6a4844e9-bf5d-43ea-9eed-6ae9cfa75ecf'),
 ('163', '137', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Allied World\",\"slug\":\"allied-world\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Since their formation in 2001, Allied World have built a reputation as a strong supplier of insurance and reinsurance solutions globally with a worldwide network of offices and a NYSE listing.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Appointed as Main Contractor, Sonica\\u2019s brief was to modernize Allied\\u2019s existing Dublin office while they remained in situ during the course of the works. The phased approach to the process involved meticulous planning with Allied\\u2019s appointed management team so that the overall programme could be broken down into daily milestones.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The scope involved increasing the level of open plan allowances in the space via. removal of existing cellular offices, M&E augmentations to supplement the additional head count, new canteen facilities, meeting facilities, floor finishes and a complete workstation package renewal.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The bulk of the works were conducted outside of normal office hours to minimize the impact to the Client\\u2019s day-to-day operations, with the Sonica Site Team delivering against every milestone in the process from start to finish.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>In Depth Planning for substantial Out of Hours workscope<\\/li><li>Upgraded M&E for increased staff head count<\\/li><li>Re-cellularisation of Manager Offices and Meeting Rooms<\\/li><li>Full new staff canteen facilities<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Custom House Quay, Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"You kept us informed through the whole process, we knew what was happening, when it was happening, what task was next in the chain and when it was successfully completed. We always felt like we were in good hands.\",\"62\":\"Aideen Quinn, VP for HR, Europe & Asia, Allied World\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>800m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>8 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:16:44', '2018-02-15 18:16:44', 'dd16aab9-bad5-46dd-8ace-8a977ad25204'),
 ('164', '138', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"SCA\",\"slug\":\"sca\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Sonica acted as traditional Main Contractor for the fitout of SCA Ireland\\u2019s new offices with responsibility for design and certification of the M&E systems forming part of the overall brief.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Taken from Landlord CAT-A condition, works involved formation of open plan offices, manager cellular offices, boardroom facilities with full A\\/V capability, new staff canteen, post room & store rooms.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We also had responsibility for securing Landlord consent for the M&E alterations involved in supplementing and modifying the A\\/C and lighting control systems to suit our finalized layouts.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Buzzifelt feature acoustic attenuation<\\/li><li>Feature graphics and wall murals<\\/li><li>M&E Design and Build<\\/li><li>Management of Client Direct furniture vendor<\\/li><li>Landlord consent applications<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Blanchardstown Corporate Park 2, Dublin 15\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"We have been very impressed with your company\\u2019s overall professionalism from the cleanliness of the site, management of contractors, general can-do attitude and most importantly; the ahead of schedule completion of the job. The new office looks fantastic and the whole team are looking forward to moving into their new home!\",\"62\":\"Simon Pickering, SCA \\/ Tork\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>400m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>4 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:16:54', '2018-02-15 18:16:54', 'a99c9789-35d1-4d54-b908-60254ef99767'),
 ('165', '139', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Cartrawler\",\"slug\":\"cartrawler\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Cartrawler provides travel-related retailers with a fully managed gateway to over 800 car rental agents at 30,000 locations in 174 different countries.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sonica completed the fitout of their new offices in Dublin comprising cellular offices, meeting rooms, staff canteens, an All Hands Town Hall meeting area, chill out room and open plan workspace to accommodate up to 235 staff.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>M&E works were carried out under a domestic sub-contract with Sonica offering a turn key project developed from initial tender drawings and specifications. Works involved supplementing the landlord A\\/C systems, a full data installation to a central comms room, electrical power distribution to desk mounted furniture solution and full lighting augmentation to include scene setting in selected areas.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Dundrum Business Park, Dublin 14\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"You took the stress out of the whole process for us \\u2013 the fitout was handed over as we wanted it when we wanted it.\",\"62\":\"Lynsey Egan, Cartrawler\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,200m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>8 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:17:08', '2018-02-15 18:17:08', '587b4f06-4301-47f4-9847-762c049281e2'),
 ('166', '140', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Lisney\",\"slug\":\"lisney\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>When relocating from their home of c. 20-years on Dublin\\u2019s St. Stephen\\u2019s Green, Lisney appointed Sonica to act as their Main Contractor and Partner to deliver their modern new office space over two floors on Earlsfort Terrace.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works involved the strip out of 2 existing floors in the building in preparation for the new office layouts. The first floor was fitted out as the Corporate Reception and Meeting space, a place for Lisney to receive their Clients, hold large meetings and conduct auctions. The second floor comprised the open plan office space, internal meeting space, staff canteen facilities, file storage and desking for 80 staff members.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were conducted on the upper floors of St. Stephens Green House, a multi tenanted office block, with all logistics and day-to-day site issues managed by the on-site Sonica Operations Team.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>High End Corporate reception area<\\/li><li>Stone flooring and bespoke branded joinery<\\/li><li>Management of Client direct Furniture and A\\/V vendors<\\/li><li>Aggressive programme delivered in multi-tenanted building<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Earlsford Terrance, Dublin 4\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Your staff were exceptionally courteous to all our sitting building tenants through the whole fitout process, we hardly noticed you were even here.\",\"62\":\"David Hogan, SSG Building Manager\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1200m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>8 weeks onsite<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:17:26', '2018-02-15 18:17:26', 'c7dd9da2-e57e-47d2-ad92-80b3ea2206fe'),
 ('167', '141', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Apollo Aviation\",\"slug\":\"apollo-aviation\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Founded in 2002, Apollo Aviation Group is a multi-strategy alternative investment firm specializing in commercial aviation investing, creating and extracting value by investing in mid-life and mature commercial aircraft and engines.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sonica were appointed as traditional Main Contractor for the fitout, which was carried out on the top floor of Connaught House, the exclusive multi-tenanted corporate HQ building off Mespil Road in Dublin 2.<br>With stunning views over Dublin, the works involved the complete strip out of the existing finishes in preparation for the new Apollo layouts. Several key building features were identified to be retained and incorporated within the completed office works, all others were promptly cleared in the opening days on site.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The completed offices comprise open plan work areas, cellular offices and meeting rooms, a bespoke Client reception area, staff canteen & break out area, full data rewire back to a new comms room, complete A\\/V & VC installation and a thorough M&E upgrade to accommodate the new layouts.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Working on the top floor of one of the most prestigious buildings in Dublin presented it\\u2019s own challenges, but through the daily co-ordination and management of works by the sitting Sonica Site Team, the project ran smoothly for start to finish. The completed office is considered by the Professional Team as one of the finest small office fitout examples conducted in Dublin in recent years.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Bespoke joinery installations to Client Reception Area & Corporate Meeting Space<\\/li><li>Identification, retention and re-use of core building fabrics to augment the fitout<\\/li><li>Complete M&E overhaul to suit new office layouts<\\/li><li>Intense co-ordination with sitting Building Management through the fitout process.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Connaught House, Burlington Road, Dublin 4\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Very easy to work with and extremely professional from start to finish. Completed the job to a very high quality on time and within budget \\u2013\\u00a0\\r\\ncouldn\\u2019t ask for any more.\",\"62\":\"Marcus Miller, VP Dublin Operations, Apollo Aviation\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>8 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-15 18:17:35', '2018-02-15 18:17:35', 'acf8cbc0-851e-49bc-8e10-e0e9e61bae58'),
 ('168', '159', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Yemisi Onasanya\",\"slug\":\"yemisi-onasanya\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"yonasanya@sonica-fitout.com\",\"66\":\"<p>My role in a nutshell involves managing all costs relating to a construction project through its entire lifecycle whilst ensuring optimum return is achieved on the project. I am responsible for managing multi-projects and undertaking all commercial duties and contract administration as required on a project.<\\/p>\",\"70\":[\"195\"],\"65\":\"Quantity Surveyor\",\"68\":\"<p>I enjoy the fast-paced nature and project variety of the fit-out market, with no two projects ever the same and with its daily challenges which keeps me on my toes. I enjoy the opportunity to form and cultivate new relationships with clients and project teams as well as the satisfaction to be part of project from inception right to its successful completion for the satisfaction of both the client and the organisation I represent.<\\/p>\",\"67\":\"<p>With over 15 years in the Construction Industry and with varied experience across different sectors and industries, I find my passion to be in the fit-out industry. Sonica Fitout provides the right avenue to make a positive and progressive contribution within a fast growing and thriving organisation. I was attracted to Sonica\\u2019s business model, its commitment to strong leadership and development and with a high order book of project, it means I can further advance my career whilst doing what I genuinely enjoy and work with a great team of other like-minded professionals.<\\/p>\"}}', '2018-02-16 01:55:07', '2018-02-16 01:55:07', '53811ac9-a9df-4433-b522-d457a89b75b7'),
 ('169', '160', '17', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"17\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Aaron Forde\",\"slug\":\"aaron-forde\",\"postDate\":1518716700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"69\":\"aforde@sonica-fitout.com\",\"66\":\"<p>As Bid manager I am responsible for the preparation of bids in response to Request for Proposals (RFPs) from potential clients. I work with all relevant stakeholders to ensure the delivery of a successful bid.<\\/p>\",\"70\":\"\",\"65\":\"Bid & Pre-Construction Manager\",\"68\":\"<p>The fact that every project is different and every client has different expectations really interests me. I really enjoy the fact that I am one of the first people to see a project design at tender stage, fresh off the drawing board.<\\/p>\",\"67\":\"<p>The opportunity to join this fast growing fit out company was a really easy decision. Its a fast moving and exciting environment to be in and the quality of projects are second to none.<\\/p>\"}}', '2018-02-16 01:55:26', '2018-02-16 01:55:26', '39873fc8-6a89-45cb-8fbc-c9429974562d'),
 ('170', '104', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Demonware\",\"slug\":\"demonware\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Demonware are an Irish software development company specialising in creating networking software and services for computer game development, most notably for the Call of Duty on-line game franchise. The company were acquired by US game publisher Activision Blizzard in 2007 and have offices in Dublin, Vancouver and Shanghai.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the complexity of the works and the fact that the offices would remain LIVE through the refurbishment, the project was bid on a 2-stage basis with an open tender process to identify two preferred bidders followed by a post-tender interview process to select their final fitout partner. A large part of the Client Team\\u2019s decision making process also centered on input and commentary from the Contractor into the initial scheme design with recommendations on buildability and value engineering. We were suitably delighted to win out at interview stage and be appointed as Demonware\\u2019s contractor of choice \\u2013 with us on board, planning for their new European HQ officially kicked-off led by international architects, Urban Agency.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The scope of works included segregation of the existing floor plate into Live \\/ Under-Construction areas, the complete strip of the demised floor areas, full M&E, IT and A\\/V installation, a bespoke fabricated solution for Meeting Rooms (made from curved glass pods) and Team Huddle Rooms (machined birch faced plywood), full soft & hard flooring, extensive graphics package and the management & supervision of the Client\\u2019s furniture vendors. Of further note was the fact that the project was completed with the Client in full occupation on the 5th Floor of a multi-tenanted building.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The finished project is a fabulous addition to our portfolio of works and is a job that we are very proud to have been involved with.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full design realisation and co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Staff migration & move management<\\/li><li>Full M&E and IT installations<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package<\\/li><li>Curved glass huddle rooms<\\/li><li>Birch-faced plywood huddle pods<\\/li><li>Exposed building structure & ceiling<\\/li><li>Corporate signage & brand identity<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"201\"],\"56\":\"Parnell Street\\r\\nDublin1\",\"64\":[\"197\",\"198\",\"200\",\"201\",\"199\"],\"61\":\"I just want take a breath to let you know how happy we\'ve been so far with how the build is being managed by your Team and with the quality of the work that is being done. Harry, Doug and Ray have been a pleasure to work with throughout these past 14 weeks. What could have been a very stressful experience for us, has turned out to be an education in how a professional renovation should run. Thanks to you and your Team for this.\",\"62\":\"Amy Smith, Business Services Manager, Demonware\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,800m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>4-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>14 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 02:35:44', '2018-02-16 02:35:44', '23f60c4e-17d6-4414-9e37-cc03abe882cc'),
