folio of works and is a job that we are very proud to have been involved with.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full design realisation and co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Staff migration & move management<\\/li><li>Full M&E and IT installations<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package<\\/li><li>Curved glass huddle rooms<\\/li><li>Birch-faced plywood huddle pods<\\/li><li>Exposed building structure & ceiling<\\/li><li>Corporate signage & brand identity<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"201\"],\"56\":\"Parnell Street\\r\\nDublin 1\",\"64\":[\"197\",\"198\",\"200\",\"201\",\"199\"],\"61\":\"I just want take a breath to let you know how happy we\'ve been so far with how the build is being managed by your Team and with the quality of the work that is being done. Harry, Doug and Ray have been a pleasure to work with throughout these past 14 weeks. What could have been a very stressful experience for us, has turned out to be an education in how a professional renovation should run. Thanks to you and your Team for this.\",\"62\":\"Amy Smith, Business Services Manager, Demonware\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,800m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>4-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>14 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 02:40:47', '2018-02-16 02:40:47', 'b22cab4e-08c2-4b0e-91aa-cfa5dcf7006b'),
 ('173', '202', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Adobe\",\"slug\":\"adobe\",\"postDate\":1518776298,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Adobe Systems Incorporated is the world leading IT platform focused upon the creation of multimedia and creativity software products, best known for Photoshop, Acrobat Reader and the Portable Document Format (PDF). With over 50 Billion Adobe Products opened from 2016, we relished the opportunity to deliver their new colour-strident office space in Dublin\\u2019s Citywest Business Campus.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our mandate was to take an existing vacant floor plate layout and transfigure it into a fully-functional and dynamic office space. The works involved the installation of all new wall partitions, floor finishes, internal decorations, M&E services installations and management of Client direct office furniture, security and AV solutions.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The design of the working environment was for a predominantly open plan space to allow for more collaborative interaction and employee connectivity with strategically placed workstations and cellular meeting spaces ensuring that teams retain their structure within the overall environment. &nbsp;Features of the project included a Games room vaulting with animated formations and modern console equipment, a combined spacious and homely Canteen \\/ Breakout area and a series of segmented Board and Meeting rooms grouped within an ostentatious catwalk.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project was delivered in 10 weeks following an accelerated pre-construction and mobilisation period to meet the Clients rigorous occupation date achievement.<\\/p><p><\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>2-Week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>10 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":\"\",\"56\":\"Citywest Business Campus\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>900m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>Bespoke specialised joinery with numerous unique finishes and materials<\\/li><li>International collaboration with&nbsp;<span class=\\\"il\\\">Adobe<\\/span>\\u2019s overseas&nbsp;steering group<\\/li><li>Corporate signage & brand identity<\\/li><li>Management of Client direct vend packages<\\/li><\\/ul><p><\\/p>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:18:18', '2018-02-16 10:18:18', 'e590a413-cf5b-40ee-85aa-abc4a24e3689'),
 ('174', '202', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Adobe\",\"slug\":\"adobe\",\"postDate\":1518776280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Adobe Systems Incorporated is the world leading IT platform focused upon the creation of multimedia and creativity software products, best known for Photoshop, Acrobat Reader and the Portable Document Format (PDF). With over 50 Billion Adobe Products opened from 2016, we relished the opportunity to deliver their new colour-strident office space in Dublin\\u2019s Citywest Business Campus.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our mandate was to take an existing vacant floor plate layout and transfigure it into a fully-functional and dynamic office space. The works involved the installation of all new wall partitions, floor finishes, internal decorations, M&E services installations and management of Client direct office furniture, security and AV solutions.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The design of the working environment was for a predominantly open plan space to allow for more collaborative interaction and employee connectivity with strategically placed workstations and cellular meeting spaces ensuring that teams retain their structure within the overall environment. &nbsp;Features of the project included a Games room vaulting with animated formations and modern console equipment, a combined spacious and homely Canteen \\/ Breakout area and a series of segmented Board and Meeting rooms grouped within an ostentatious catwalk.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project was delivered in 10 weeks following an accelerated pre-construction and mobilisation period to meet the Clients rigorous occupation date achievement.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>2-Week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>10 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"203\"],\"56\":\"Citywest Business Campus\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>900m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>Bespoke specialised joinery with numerous unique finishes and materials<\\/li><li>International collaboration with&nbsp;Adobe\\u2019s overseas&nbsp;steering group<\\/li><li>Corporate signage & brand identity<\\/li><li>Management of Client direct vend packages<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:22:00', '2018-02-16 10:22:00', '390d84eb-23d9-4608-85ce-e8b3c8844430'),
 ('175', '102', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"21 Charlemont\",\"slug\":\"21-charlemont\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Rohan Holdings is a leader in the complex business of developing prestige offices, high quality business parks and industrial premises. With over 40 years\\u2019 experience in land acquisition, design, planning, construction and tenant fit out, Rohan Holdings have a respected proven track record of delivering projects on time, within budget and to their clients\\u2019 satisfaction.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Working in the shell of the newly completed 21 Charlemont Place Office Block, our brief was to take the \\u201cGrey Box\\u201d finish to full Landlord CAT-A standard to LEED Gold and A3 BER Rating.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Set against an aggressive time line driven by a signed single tenancy lease for the whole building, works included complete raised floor installation, soft floor finishes, partitions and ceilings, joinery and decorations. Our brief also extended the the complete M&E installations to include A\\/C, lighting, protective services, basement and roof plant, louvres & screening with full testing and commissioning.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Cat A Office Fitout<\\/li><li>Extensive Green Roof<\\/li><li>LEED Gold Certification and A3 BER<\\/li><li>Balconies and Feature Roof Terrace<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"204\"],\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>3,420m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>2-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>10 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:22:08', '2018-02-16 10:22:08', '8f064366-a164-4df9-ae3e-0fe0004ef2a3'),
 ('176', '103', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>We are delighted to showcase the successful completion of a new 15k sq.ft. Corporate HQ office in Dublin\\u2019s City Centre for a Private Sonica Client, the results of which are absolutely stunning.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our brief took the project from an existing Landlord CAT-A finish (which was fully stripped out) to their fitted out Corporate HQ in 8 weeks from commencement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were undertaken in a multi-tenanted office development with continual intensive daily co-ordination with the sitting Building Management Team. Added to the time sensitive nature of the project was the Client\\u2019s \\u201cnot-to-exceed\\u201d occupation date which was a key consideration in our aggressive construction programme.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the high degree of cellularisation to form the various offices, meeting spaces and executive boardrooms, the mechanical scope required considerable addition to the primary Landlord ventilation provisions via. intensive upgrades, modelling and building control integration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project scope also included a large specialist joinery component, extensive meeting spaces with feature exposed ceilings and feature lighting throughout, bespoke reception area, feature hard and soft floorings, substantial active IT solution, a fully redundant IT backbone install to main comms room, high-end Corporate level access control and security install, A\\/V delivery and a full furniture installation across the complete floor plate.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li><sub>Design and VE development to suit budget parameters<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>International collaboration with multiple project stakeholders<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Co-ordination with local Team on relocation deliverables<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Comms room commissioned and complete 2 weeks before handover to allow Client IT access.<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Live building environment<br><\\/sub><\\/li><li><sub>Full M&E data & VC co-ordination<\\/sub><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"206\"],\"56\":\"Dublin 4\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,500m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>7 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:22:14', '2018-02-16 10:22:14', '1c8b5376-b3e8-492f-8dc5-f32650049e2d'),
 ('177', '105', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Hubspot\",\"slug\":\"hubspot\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>We had the tremendous fortune to meet with and work alongside our friends in Hubspot when our MD PM\\u2019d their very first Dublin office for just 8-people five short years ago.&nbsp; Since then, we\\u2019ve had the distinct honour to be part of their expansion year-on-year as the Sonica Team continued to service their ever increasing head count and office space requirements.&nbsp; Their growth in Dublin has been simply astounding.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>It is therefore with great pride, and shared enthusiasm for their continued future successes, that we announce the completion and launch of their new EMEA HQ in Dublin, which was opened in March 2016 with substantial (and well deserved) fanfare across the Irish media.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We look forward to working with Hubspot as their PM of choice here in Dublin, and wish them every good fortune in their fabulous new home. #HubSpotDigsDublin<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full Design Realisation and Co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Landlord Approval and Grant of Licence to Alter<\\/li><li>Local Design Team Appointment & Management as Lead Consultant<\\/li><li>Complete Project Financial Control & Package Management<\\/li><li>Client Direct Vendor Engagement and Management<\\/li><li>Staff Migration & Move Management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"207\"],\"56\":\"Dublin 1\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Sonica has been a phenomenal partner to HubSpot - they always keep our interests front-and-centre and are beyond timely and thorough. If you wanted a partner that can do it all and give the attention these complex fitout projects command, it is Sonica Fitout - they simply get it, and get results.\",\"62\":\"Ken Papa, Facilities Director, Hubspot Inc.\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>2,750m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>12 weeks Design Co-ordination, Contract Formulation & Lease Management<\\/li><li>10 weeks Build Management On-Site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:22:21', '2018-02-16 10:22:21', '10aa57dc-189e-42d6-b0fd-9f134523b25d'),
 ('178', '106', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client-1\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Our brief was to strip and refit the old Anglo Irish Bank space over two floors in St. Stephen\\u2019s Green House and transform it into an expansive, sophisticated, tech-savvy office for our Client\\u2019s expanded new HQ in Ireland.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were executed on a 10-week programme within a fully engaged, heavily trafficked, multi-tenanted building. With it\\u2019s location in the heart of Dublin\\u2019s shopping district on the iconic St. Stephen\\u2019s Green, the delivery of the finished project on an accelerated timeline formed a hugely important part of our project execution plan where the delivery \\/ collection logistics, overall traffic management, DCC liaison, out of hours works scheduling and compliance with strict building noise restrictions all required in-depth consideration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Architectural Design included a substantial joinery package, multiple floor finishes, open grid exposed ceilings, extensive Client direct vend supervision and migration management. Other packages included substantial upgrades to the Mechanical, Electrical, IT and AV installations with all service works demanding a high level of co-ordinated attention to guarantee that the vision for the completed space was realised.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Large open plan spaces with extensive perimeter cellularisation.<\\/li><li>Extensive M&E & IT package with \\u201copen grid\\u201d M&E ceiling services<\\/li><li>Engagement of specialist contractors to facilitate works in a time restricted programme.<\\/li><li>Co-ordination with local teams and stakeholders on relocation deliverables.<\\/li><li>Cost and VE development to suit strict budget parameters.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"209\"],\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>3,000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>10 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:22:28', '2018-02-16 10:22:28', '41c75878-cbff-4489-9686-dc9a5f8fc4e1'),
 ('179', '107', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"UDG Healthcare\",\"slug\":\"udg-healthcare\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Designed by RKD Interiors, our brief took the assignment from an Existing Landlord CAT-A area over 2-separate tenancies, both of which were then fully stripped back to basic shell and core structure as part of our works, to become UDG Healthcare\\u2019s Corporate HQ within a 10-week period from Commencement on site.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were performed unobtrusively within a fully engaged, highly trafficked, multi-tenanted building with close overlap to Campus Management, Client Stakeholders and neighbouring tenants.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Packages encompassed a sizeable stylish joinery element and complex Mechanical, Electrical & IT upgrades to service the open-plan work-space areas and segmental modular offices & meeting rooms. The main Reception features an inviting design element luring to a quirky \\u2018Breakout Area Canteen\\u2019 with feature brick internal facades, critall glazed screens, floating \\u2018wooden\\u2019 acoustic ceilings and matchless tiled flooring.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the nature and scale of the sharp trapezoidal shaped walls and ceilings, paired with the diverging display of flooring and wall colours, the detailing in the Architectural packages required a Sonica level of attention to guarantee that the Architects vision for the completed space was realised.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Design and VE development to suit strict budget parameters<\\/li><li>Comms room commissioned and complete 3 weeks before handover to allow Client IT access<\\/li><li>Liaison and management of Client Direct vendors<\\/li><li>Project acceleration to ensure no client \\u2018down-time\\u2019 and smooth, quick turn-around on staff migrations<\\/li><li>Co-ordination with local Team on relocation deliverables<\\/li><li>M&E and IT upgrades throughout<\\/li><li>Turnkey furniture package<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"210\"],\"56\":\"Citywest Business Campus\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"It was great to work with Hugh Ward and his team at Sonica Fitout on our new HQ in Riverwalk, Citywest. We were very impressed with the level of professionalism and attention to detail on every aspect of this project which produced a high standard of finish. Sonica Fitouts commitment to this project ensured that it came in on programme and within budget. Everyone is delighted with the final result.\",\"62\":\"Donal Burke, Head of Procurement\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1,250m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-Con<\\/li><li>10 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:22:34', '2018-02-16 10:22:34', '106d3a7f-4782-42f7-9356-68668856832e'),
 ('180', '108', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"3 Arena\",\"slug\":\"3-arena\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Full D&B project from receipt of Client outline brief to final delivery and handover. Development of a central defined theme to roll out across the complete rebrand project was the key deliverable.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>1672 individual ceiling suspended \\u201cCities\\u201d in the 4th floor bar, over 2,400 individually controlled LED lights per City (and that\\u2019s just one area on one floor..!)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3m dia. \\u201cOculus\\u201d video back-projected onto VIP ceiling \\u2013 video specifically commissioned for the Kaleidoscope Bar fitout.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fully programmable KNX Lighting system with user defined colour and dimming set points depending on event and scene setting requirements. This linked back to main venue DALI system for central control by Venue management.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fully interactive Twitter feed linked to feature \\u201cfloating Megalopolis\\u201d to allow visitors Tweet their venue experiences directly into the bars in real time.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Conceptual development and full project design<\\/li><li>GMP Contract Sum<\\/li><li>Intricate project programming<\\/li><li>Live venue interaction & co-ordination<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"205\"],\"56\":\"North Wall Quay, Dublin 1\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Have to say it looks absolutely incredible. Proud to have worked on such a prestigious project for such a prestigious company as\\r\\nSonica Fitout. From all at Devlin in Design. Congratulations to Sonica.\",\"62\":\"Enda Devlin, Devlin in Design\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>4000m2 overall Venue Area.<\\/li><li>Works spread across three separate project sites running concurrently.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>8 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:22:38', '2018-02-16 10:22:38', 'f0713ef2-4f04-4017-bdef-c875ef939ef9'),
 ('181', '109', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Salesforce\",\"slug\":\"salesforce\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Salesforce&nbsp;is the world\\u2019s leading CRM software and enterprise cloud ecosystem, their \\u201cCustomer Success Platform\\u201d helps businesses grow into a more streamlined, effective and efficient organisations across sales, service, marketing and more.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Sonica Ops Team has had the pleasure of being part of SFDC\\u2019s expansion by servicing their ever increasing head count and office space requirements for the past 3-years.&nbsp; It is therefore with great pride that we showcase the latest SFDC office completion, a 15,000 sq.ft. floor plate in Central Park.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works involved the demolition and strip out of the previous tenant\\u2019s existing fitted offices to cater for the new Salesforce remodelled floor plate layout.&nbsp; The office design placed emphasis on increased Team collaboration with all new open plan workstations, meeting rooms, offices, boardrooms, flexible spaces, staff kitchens & canteen areas, breakout areas and a number of bespoke \\u201cTechForce Bars\\u201d all part of the required brief.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>They have since been voted Ireland\\u2019s Best Workplace \\u2013 the company was ranked No. 1 on the list of the Best Large Places to Work, a ranking based on employees\\u2019 own assessments of their experiences.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Full GMP Build Delivery<\\/li><li>Extensive Feature Joinery Package procurement<\\/li><li>Complete staff auditorium with extensive A\\/V<\\/li><li>Client Direct Vendor Engagement and Management<\\/li><li>Staff Migration & Move Management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"212\"],\"56\":\"Central Park, Dublin 18\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"Just a little note to say a BIG thank you to you and all the Sonica team. It was a real pleasure working with you all. Thanks for your guidance, assistance and patience! Fingers crossed for the next one.\",\"62\":\"Cathy Mooney, Senior Office Manager\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1500m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>10 weeks Design Co-ordination, Procurement, GMP Formulation<\\/li><li>12 weeks Build Management On-Site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:26:05', '2018-02-16 10:26:05', 'cecad75a-8b9d-4316-a1e8-4fd501942b18'),
 ('182', '110', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Wipro\",\"slug\":\"wipro\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Since entering the Irish market in 2015, WIPRO have gone from strength to strength securing substantial projects for their ever increasing Client base. This success has been met with a rapid increase in head count and exponential office space requirement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Having already completed over 50k sq.ft. of office space in Dublin for WIPRO since 2015, we were delighted to build upon and advance the great working relationship we had developed with both their International and Local Teams when they appointed us again as their Turnkey D&B Fitout Specialist for their new expansion offices in Ballsbridge.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were undertaken in a multi-tenanted office development with continual intensive daily co-ordination with the sitting Campus Management Team. Added to the time sensitive nature of the project was the Client\\u2019s \\u201cnot-to-exceed\\u201d occupation date which was a key consideration in our aggressive construction programme.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Due to the high degree of cellularisation to form the various offices, meeting spaces, VC Rooms & Executive Boardrooms, the mechanical scope required considerable addition to the primary Landlord ventilation provisions via. intensive upgrades, modelling and building control integration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The project scope also included a large specialist joinery component, exposed ceilings and feature lighting throughout, feature hard and soft floorings, substantial active IT solution, a fully redundant IT backbone install with UPS back up to main comms room, high-end Corporate level access control and security install, A\\/V delivery and a full furniture installation across the complete floor plate.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Sonica PM<\\/li><li>Full Design Realisation and Co-ordination with International Design Team<\\/li><li>Landlord Approval and Grant of Licence to Alter<\\/li><li>Local Design Team Appointment & Management as Lead Consultant<\\/li><li>Complete Project Financial Control & Package Management<\\/li><li>Client Direct Vendor Engagement and Management<\\/li><li>Staff Migration & Move Management<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"213\"],\"56\":\"Ballsbridge\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>1000m2<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-construction<\\/li><li>8 weeks on-site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:26:13', '2018-02-16 10:26:13', 'b7a8ebbf-bb87-411d-a278-c6cd077ba41f'),
 ('183', '111', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client-2\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Sonica Fitout were contracted to completely refurbish the Ground Floor lobby of the headquarters of one of Ireland\\u2019s leading providers of wealth management and financial advisory services. Clients of this prestigious private client are used to a meticulous attention to detail and as such this was reflected in the design and level of finish expected.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The intent was to provide enclosed, private areas throughout the space with which to hold impromptu, private meetings while maintaining a bright, open and modern feel throughout. Combined with the extremely well-appointed joinery package the overall feel of the space was one of practical opulence and luxury.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The scope of works was a complete refurbishment with curved recessed bulkheads all LED backlit, stone tiling throughout, new security gates and curved glazed meeting rooms all surrounding the walnut clad lift core that integrated seamlessly with an oversized reception desk. In addition new bathroom and kitchen facilities were completed as well as all new air conditioning throughout the floor.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Following a week\\u2019s pre construction this project was delivered in 5 weeks over multiple phases keeping live access available to staff members 24 hours a day 7 days a week with minimal disruption.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Natural Stone floor<\\/li><li>Bespoke Walnut wall cladding<\\/li><li>Curved glazed partitions throughout<\\/li><li>Oversized feature reception desk<\\/li><li>Backlit feature ceilings throughout<\\/li><li>New staff \\u201cspeedlanes\\u201d<\\/li><li>New facilities<\\/li><li>Completely revamped AC system.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"211\"],\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"62\":\"\",\"58\":\"<ul><li>Reception areas<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"59\":\"<ul><li>1-week Pre-Con<\\/li><li>5 weeks on site<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}}', '2018-02-16 10:26:18', '2018-02-16 10:26:18', '4d0bbb35-71c7-4980-a1f7-852e0a777a55'),
 ('184', '106', '16', '1', 'en_ie', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"16\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Private Client\",\"slug\":\"private-client-1\",\"postDate\":1518716640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"57\":\"<p>Our brief was to strip and refit the old Anglo Irish Bank space over two floors in St. Stephen\\u2019s Green House and transform it into an expansive, sophisticated, tech-savvy office for our Client\\u2019s expanded new HQ in Ireland.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Works were executed on a 10-week programme within a fully engaged, heavily trafficked, multi-tenanted building. With it\\u2019s location in the heart of Dublin\\u2019s shopping district on the iconic St. Stephen\\u2019s Green, the delivery of the finished project on an accelerated timeline formed a hugely important part of our project execution plan where the delivery \\/ collection logistics, overall traffic management, DCC liaison, out of hours works scheduling and compliance with strict building noise restrictions all required in-depth consideration.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Architectural Design included a substantial joinery package, multiple floor finishes, open grid exposed ceilings, extensive Client direct vend supervision and migration management. Other packages included substantial upgrades to the Mechanical, Electrical, IT and AV installations with all service works demanding a high level of co-ordinated attention to guarantee that the vision for the completed space was realised.<\\/p>\",\"60\":\"<ul><li>Large open plan spaces with extensive perimeter cellularisation.<\\/li><li>Extensive M&E & IT package with \\u201copen grid\\u201d M&E ceiling services<\\/li><li>Engagement of specialist contractors to facilitate works in a time restricted programme.<\\/li><li>Co-ordination with local teams and stakeholders on relocation deliverables.<\\/li><li>Cost and VE development to suit strict budget parameters.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"63\":[\"208\"],\"56\":\"Dublin 2\",\"64\":\"\",\"61\":\"\",\"6